<P>
METRO DIGEST / LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF: MAN FOUND SHOT TO DEATH BEHIND BUS BENCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A 49-year-old West Los Angeles man was found shot to death Friday morning 
behind a bus bench at Santa Monica and Westwood boulevards. 
</P>
<P>
The body of Carlos Armando Berrara was discovered by a passer-by who notified 
police, according to Detective Lee Kingsford of the Los Angeles Police 
Department's West Los Angeles station. 
</P>
<P>
Kingsford said no witnesses had been found and there was no indication of why 
Berrara was slain. 
</P>
