<P>
GRAFFITI; VANDALISM; LEVITZ FURNITURE CORP; GLENDALE (CA); MURALS; 
DEMONSTRATIONS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; VALLEY ORGANIZED IN COMMUNITY EFFORTS; 
BUSINESS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
