<HEADLINE>
<P>
HE'S FEELING GOOD ABOUT BASEBALL AGAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Just when you think the grand ol' game is heading to the dogs, an article about 
the likes of Chuck Essegian and Little Red warms my heart like the spring sun 
warms the grass at Vero Beach. 
</P>
<P>
Can we send a copy to every current major league ballplayer to remind them of 
what it takes to be a big leaguer? There's a little bit of Little Red in all of 
us, no matter how old we are. Thanks, Mr. Essegian. 
</P>
<P>
BILL PIKE, Carlsbad 
</P>
</TEXT>
