doubled in a run for St. Francis in a nonleague game at La Salle. St. Francis 
sophomore Jose Cevera allowed two hits and two runs in four innings but was 
relieved in the fifth by Manny Fernandez (4-2), who yielded the winning run an 
inning later. 
</P>
<P>
Hoover 9, Muir 7 (nine innings) -- Mickey Moreno had two hits and knocked in 
